(fifthQuint)Prospective Study to Evaluate Safety of Deb-TACE With 100 Beads in Patients With Non Resectable HCC.

 In this observational, prospective study patients will undergo DEB-TACE and subsequent follow up procedures according to standard clinical practice.

 The primary aim of the study is to describe treatment safety and tolerability of 100 mu beads in DEB-TACE.

 As a secondary end-point a description of efficacy parameters will be obtained.

